@5002 = ~Silent, semi-translucent flames surge the length of the blade as it clears its scabbard. This two-handed sword is a common weapon for servants of devils involved in the eternal Blood War, harnessing the flames of the Nine Hells with such potency that it can burn through even the most resistant of foe. How it ended up here is anyone's guess, but having such a weapon in one's possession in undoubtedly a dangerous affair.

