– Additionally, each hit inflicts a -1% weakness to piercing damage (cumulative) for 5 rounds.

THAC0: +3
Damage: 1d4+3, +1 slashing damage
Damage type: Piercing
Speed Factor: 0
Proficiency Type: Dagger
